# ── Local Supabase config ──────────────────────────────────
# Holds the project URL and anon key. Anon keys are public-safe
# (they're served to every browser), but we keep this file out
# of git so forks/clones don't accidentally inherit someone
# else's project. Each developer creates their own supabase.js
# from the template in the README.

# ── Environment / secrets (in case any get added later) ────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.pem
*.key

# ── OS junk ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Editor / IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Logs / build noise ─────────────────────────────────────
*.log
node_modules/
dist/
build/
